{"about_the_game":"Medieval Fantasy was a surge of inspiration, which came with the emergence of artwork created by robots.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI've been wanting to test my writing on a Visual Novel for a while, so this new technology was the excuse I needed to create this adventure, which simulates a tabletop RPG session with friends.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIt's a short story, with some ramifications that might spark interest in replaying from the beginning to see all the possible interactions.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis game is also a personal experience, to see the acceptance of the Brazilian public with Visual Novels, and to see the shortest possible time that I could create a game from beginning to end.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf your experience is worthwhile, consider purchasing the deluxe edition, which comes with extra high-res images and a Thank you letter.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThanks for reading this far, I hope you enjoy the game!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Steps","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2150510/876d1f4da310f42ca00e94e383cc79df00e50eb8.jpg"},{"name":"The History","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2150510/876d1f4da310f42ca00e94e383cc79df00e50eb8.jpg"},{"name":"Barbecue","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2150510/876d1f4da310f42ca00e94e383cc79df00e50eb8.jpg"},{"name":"Nice Battle!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2150510/876d1f4da310f42ca00e94e383cc79df00e50eb8.jpg"},{"name":"Thief","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2150510/876d1f4da310f42ca00e94e383cc79df00e50eb8.jpg"},{"name":"Ending","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2150510/876d1f4da310f42ca00e94e383cc79df00e50eb8.jpg"},{"name":"Elf+","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2150510/876d1f4da310f42c